{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与胡铁花分析画眉鸟与柳无眉的关系，推断柳无眉夫妇为寻找楚留香而接触蓉儿等人。二人抵达姑苏虎丘，途中遭遇卖花女伪装的刺客袭击，楚留香识破阴谋并夺下藏有毒针的茉莉花球。在虎丘剑池、千人石等景点，柳无眉讲述当地传说，楚留香与之周旋试探，暗藏杀机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那刺客若是他们买来的，他们为何要杀他?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是为了要杀人灭口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但将我诱出去的人，却是画眉鸟，画眉鸟也和他们是同路的么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想必也知道画眉鸟是别人化名改扮的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你怎知画眉鸟不是他们化名改扮的呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他既然要害你，是要你报答什么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你见到画眉鸟，并没有动手杀他，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当然不能杀他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么一定要怀疑柳无眉是画眉鸟呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这其中自然有许多原因。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但至少那用'暴雨梨花钉'打你的人，总不会是他们吧?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何不会是他们?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为那时他们明明还在屋子里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看到他们了么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽未看到，但明明听到他们在说话。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你并没有听到他们在'说话'，你只是听到他们在不断挣扎、呼喊和呻吟，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人在呼喊呻吟时，声音都会因痛苦而改变的，所以我们就算听出他们的声音有些不对，也不会在意，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道那时他们两人已不在屋子里，那声音只是别人装出来的?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这难道不可能?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我还是不明白，也不相信。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说来听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们怎会遇到蓉儿的呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿她们要找我，自然要先回家去看看，像她们那样的人，走在路上自然很引人注目，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼!你这算是捧我，还是骂我?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳无眉要想自甜儿口中问我的消息，自然并不困难……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她只有这一点线索，只有去碰碰运气了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但蓉儿她们为何没有一齐去，反而到了'拥翠山庄'呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她们也许是被骗，也许是被劫，也许……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道是说，蓉儿她们根本不在'拥翠山庄'，而且说不定已遭了柳无眉夫妇的毒手?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但以时间推算，她才一到沙漠，就找着我们了，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李玉函既是江南的世家子，怎会对沙漠的地形那样熟悉?何况，石观音的住处又是那么秘密，他们怎能一下子就找到了呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我还有两样想不通的事，这就是其中之一。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有一样呢?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在想不通这夫妇两人为何一定要我的命?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在，他们既已知道你对他们起了怀疑，且一定看出你昨天晚上是在装病，你的处境岂非就更危险了么?",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们难道要等你到了'拥翠山庄'后再出手?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来想必是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然知道，还要去送死?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我能不去么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，你自然不能将蓉儿她们抛在那里，可是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何以见得?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以李家在江湖中的声势，他们要暗算我，也只能在别的地方，用别人做替死鬼，到了'拥翠山庄'后，这些卑鄙的手段，他们怎敢再用出来?他们怎敢将'拥翠山庄'数十年的侠名毁于一旦?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已想通了么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你早就该想到的，除了李家子弟之外，又还有谁能得到那么珍贵的暗器?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了富甲江南的李家子弟外，又有谁一出手就能花二十万两银子?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我却情愿要二十万两银子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为她们的脚生得比别处的人漂亮，若不多让人瞧瞧，岂非暴殄天物?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卖花女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好香好香的茉莉花，公子爷买两朵吧!",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是花香?还是你的手香?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "公子爷真会说笑话，世上哪有多刺的茉莉花?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看你这老色鬼，把人家小姑娘吓成这样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若不将她骇走，她就要了你我的命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "毒针?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是我接得快，只要她的小手一甩，你我此刻还想有命么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次你又是怎么看出来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些小姑娘从小就在这条道上卖花，可见都是穷苦人家的孩子，白天卖花，晚上还得帮着做家事，哪里会有她那么样又白又嫩的手?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这双贼眼实在太厉害了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看这小姑娘也是他夫妻派来的么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不入虎穴，焉得虎子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不是虎子，是虎女。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "故老相传，昔日吴王阉间在这里造坟墓，用了工匠千人，等到墓成之后，吴王怕他们泄漏墓中的机关秘密，就把这一千人全都活埋在这石头下，所以这石头就叫做",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那石台又是什么呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么样一个仙子般的美女，真会是杀人的凶手么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说这名字还有个来历。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "楚兄既然知道这是天下第五泉，可知道天下第三泉也在这里么?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_ran_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "突然一人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜江山虽依旧，人面却已全非了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    }
